    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/smooth-spine/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=557594796969952389&sectionId=557600800294044805)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCV207Kj_0_text","label":"ggCV207Kj_0_text","default":"Leading Physical Therapy Specialist:<br><strong>This Is The Best Way to Sleep Pain-Free Through The Night</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggwXhZ_420E_customText","label":"ggwXhZ_420E_customText","default":"By Dr. Jessica Adams |"},{"type":"html","id":"ggKew72AURf_text","label":"ggKew72AURf_text","default":"&nbsp;| 10:35 am EST"},{"type":"html","id":"ggFljwOTtrJ_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggFljwOTtrJ_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-def8ccf0-d59b-414a-948d-e4a70a350648.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggX5_J7mAid_text","label":"ggX5_J7mAid_text","default":"<p><strong>1 in 2 side sleepers will experience hip pain and back discomfort which may take away their mobility and freedom </strong>— However, a breakthrough pillow, trusted by Medical Professionals, is helping people beat the statistics and even avoid back and hip surgery.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggbHP1NuO1u_youtubeUrl","label":"ggbHP1NuO1u_youtubeUrl","default":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M"},{"type":"html","id":"ggbHP1NuO1u_vimeoUrl","label":"ggbHP1NuO1u_vimeoUrl","default":"https://vimeo.com/347119375"},{"type":"html","id":"ggbHP1NuO1u_html5Url","label":"ggbHP1NuO1u_html5Url","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/bbd47457084442119a0bd4463d44b2c8.mp4"},{"type":"html","id":"ggzu6LiSpnK_text","label":"ggzu6LiSpnK_text","default":"1. Proven To Relieve Hips &amp; Back for Uninterrupted Sleep"},{"type":"html","id":"ggla3kHKFiO_text","label":"ggla3kHKFiO_text","default":"<p>Life is too short to endure constant back and hip pain, toss and turn through sleepless nights, or to struggle with painful conditions like Sciatica.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow is <strong>proven to alleviate</strong> back pain, hip pain, and Sciatica <strong>from night</strong> one, allowing you to <strong>sleep pain-free</strong> through the night.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>With the SmoothSpine Pillow, getting relief is as easy as placing it between your legs and laying on your side like usual! No complicated stretches, no doctor visits, and no medication required!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg88wNHD2_t_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg88wNHD2_t_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-f18f847e-f518-4637-9c26-f1f15d852259.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYtIuuoPmn_text","label":"ggYtIuuoPmn_text","default":"2. Wake Up Feeling Refreshed &amp; Pain-Free"},{"type":"html","id":"ggX-xoeTQ_N_text","label":"ggX-xoeTQ_N_text","default":"<p>The SmoothSpine pillow is here to help you get back to restful pain-free sleep so you can <strong>get back to enjoying the activities you love.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;<br>SmoothSpine offers a remarkable solution that not only relieves discomfort at night, but also <strong>restores your freedom</strong> to engage in the activities you love and the pain-free life you deserve during the day.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRrnXdWN2H_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggRrnXdWN2H_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-b9aeac10-d7f2-4288-aa12-4ab9a591aa5c.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gggTzEwK79l_text","label":"gggTzEwK79l_text","default":"3. Soft Elastic Strap for All Night Support"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_KzlHZdOq_text","label":"gg_KzlHZdOq_text","default":"<p>The SmoothSpine Pillow comes with a soft elastic strap that <strong>keeps it securely between your legs all night long.</strong> No more waking up to readjust or losing support while you sleep—just consistent comfort and proper spinal alignment until morning.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggrrIRkF26V_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggrrIRkF26V_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-edfd481e-22b4-48f6-bc7a-b4b4dd83ccc0.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggEZQk3xrCO_text","label":"ggEZQk3xrCO_text","default":"4. Helps with Sciatica and Herniated Discs"},{"type":"html","id":"gglMiGy7ZPH_text","label":"gglMiGy7ZPH_text","default":"<p>The SmoothSpine pillow is specifically designed to address various conditions such as Sciatica, Bursitis, Piriformis, Stenosis, and Herniated Discs.</p><p><br>By providing comfortable all night support and <strong>proper spinal alignment,</strong> the SmoothSpine pillow helps to actively <strong>alleviate pinched nerves, stiff joints, and tense muscles,</strong> leading to better hip, lower back, and even knee health.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggG3FWVBI0S_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggG3FWVBI0S_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-a97c62b7-186e-4c92-8482-b88de795bd4a.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggoPExtW6HM_text","label":"ggoPExtW6HM_text","default":"5. Restful Sleep Without Harmful Pills or Expensive Therapy"},{"type":"html","id":"ggm9cQ1wonD_text","label":"ggm9cQ1wonD_text","default":"<p>Unlike other solutions such as harmful painkillers or invasive treatments the SmoothSpine pillow delivers <strong>natural &amp; easy pain relief.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>And while typical therapy sessions may set you back $100s each month, the SmoothSpine pillow provides a similar effectiveness at <strong>a fraction of the cost</strong>—making it accessible to everyone. This pillow lasts for years, making it the perfect <strong>long-term solution!</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>By keeping the spine and hips in their natural alignment and taking pressure off the joints and nerves, the SmoothSpine pillow supports the body in its self-healing process. Meaning you can experience <strong>natural relief free from any side effects.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZBm_S9-cn_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggZBm_S9-cn_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-7717aa79-d00a-49c4-bf32-88ed7f7537e3.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggKL2lcxy6g_text","label":"ggKL2lcxy6g_text","default":"6. Easy To Clean Case"},{"type":"html","id":"gg3RFdVOp8B_text","label":"gg3RFdVOp8B_text","default":"<p>SmoothSpine pillows are made with an easy to use <strong>zipper pillow case.</strong> Cleaning them is as simple as unzipping the case and putting it in the washing machine.&nbsp;</p><p><br>Enjoy a <strong>fresh, hygienic pillow night after night.</strong> No more worrying about sweat, dust, or odors.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg49oXMV4pL_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg49oXMV4pL_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-f7da2e8a-653b-4e70-8ea9-52ccfec22b2d.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"gg8OM3Hr3mT_text","label":"gg8OM3Hr3mT_text","default":"7. 3x More Effective Than Any Other Pillow"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7IP3cwBPT_text","label":"gg7IP3cwBPT_text","default":"<p>Many people have tried to sleep with an old pillow between their legs, often without much success. You either lose it at night, don’t support your body properly, or simply get annoyed by how big and awkward it is.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The SmoothSpine pillow is <strong>designed to be used in between your legs,</strong> stays with you all night, and <strong>doesn’t take up any additional space in bed.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>This results in longer lasting relief, uninterrupted sleep, and more comfort.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggWkglvPhgS_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggWkglvPhgS_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-8f9ab627-964a-4734-9f9f-91d653d0ea4f.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggww9BeDgxx_text","label":"ggww9BeDgxx_text","default":"8. Doctor-Recommended Pillow"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMrUy5jEMY_text","label":"ggMrUy5jEMY_text","default":"<p>Experts of the industry have been <strong>praising our pillows for the last couple of months.</strong> Many have recommended us to their friends and families.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>One special advocate for the pillow from SmoothSpine is a senior woman who suffered from Sciatica, Amanda Rowens.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><i>\"My pain started 8 years ago. I used to suffer for days, sometimes weeks.<strong> Sciatic pain really makes your life much more difficult.</strong> I would wake up during the middle of the night due to my shooting back pain. Then, the tingling started... I tried all the alternative treatments. Physical therapy. Acupuncture. Vitamins. Supplements. <strong>I WISH SmoothSpine was around back then...\"</strong></i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggadmoj4J82_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggadmoj4J82_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-4707ccb5-137c-41df-9fd3-0baf6e899bb2.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggFqWwmKcwU_text","label":"ggFqWwmKcwU_text","default":"9. 100% No Questions Asked 90-Night Money Back Guarantee"},{"type":"html","id":"ggBnzAQUEWT_text","label":"ggBnzAQUEWT_text","default":"<p>We're so confident you'll love the SmoothSpine pillow, you can <strong>try it risk-free for 90 nights.</strong> If you're not satisfied in any way, simply reach out to our helpful support team, and we’ll refund you every penny you paid, <strong>no questions asked.</strong> And with our extremely low return rate of less than 1%, we think it’s highly unlikely you will….</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggjSCFHxcxt_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggjSCFHxcxt_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-c9b6aeb8-f886-436a-b38b-a6a5c624ece1.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggIt8i12XPA_text","label":"ggIt8i12XPA_text","default":"10. Over 87,619+ Happy Side-Sleepers and Counting!"},{"type":"html","id":"ggi3qXOfJcy_text","label":"ggi3qXOfJcy_text","default":"<p>Don't just take our word for it—listen to the stories of those who have found relief with the SmoothSpine Pillow.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Sarah Anderson, an active grandmother, said this: <i><strong>“This was my best purchase ever.</strong> Before, I used a regular pillow but that never stays in place when I move and it wakes me every time. Now I finally get out of bed without a sore back and get way better sleep.”</i></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Vickie Gow, a full-time nurse, <strong>described it as her “magic pillow”</strong> that allows her to sleep pain-free after long shifts. And with an <strong>average review rating of 4.8/5,</strong> you can join thousands of happy side sleepers and experience the relief for yourself.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqQxEPMq4Q_text","label":"ggqQxEPMq4Q_text","default":"How To Get The Best Results At The Best Price Possible!<br><i>(+2 FREE Gifts!)</i>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg3l62a0Vyu_text","label":"gg3l62a0Vyu_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">Right now, the <strong>SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow</strong> is ONLY available on the brand's website.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">⚠️ We're offering a <strong>special introductory limited-time offer</strong> with a massive discount of over 50% off.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><strong>Step 1:</strong> Order your <strong>SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow</strong> today to secure a 50% discount (while supplies last).</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><strong>Step 2:</strong> Once your SmoothSpine Pillow arrives, you will experience way less pain in the morning and sleep better from the first night.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><strong>Step 3:</strong> Sleep with your <strong>Alignment Pillow from SmoothSpine</strong> all night for lasting comfort, support, and restful uninterrupted sleep. Enjoy your day feeling full of energy.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">Helpful Hint: If you have a side sleeper in your life, consider giving it as a gift - the gift of comfort, support, and the freedom to enjoy life without being limited by restless nights or nagging pain. They deserve the best sleep and pain-free living.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggKtYz4YQv5_label","label":"ggKtYz4YQv5_label","default":"<p>CLICK HERE TO CHECK THE PRICE AND AVAILABILITY 👉</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gga6HE_Av3K_text","label":"gga6HE_Av3K_text","default":"Recommended:"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMy_bqlok-_text","label":"ggMy_bqlok-_text","default":"★★★★★"},{"type":"html","id":"ggIZqcMtBmI_text","label":"ggIZqcMtBmI_text","default":"<p>4.8 | 5.467 Reviews</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggklYJAk9FD_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggklYJAk9FD_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-bec6d771-19d3-4ec1-b3c8-e7701c6e94a0.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggkfZRTAiJe_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggkfZRTAiJe_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-a9fffab6-57c3-4463-b1ec-0bae38ecd1bb.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggJb-ooU-tN_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggJb-ooU-tN_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-ae575e83-8abf-432a-a9c2-496241638984.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggmlAXCZy73_text","label":"ggmlAXCZy73_text","de